    direct-to-main allowed for solo).</li>
  <li><strong>#690 / #665</strong> — empirical backing for "composable, configurable methodology on a
    strong standard," and the explicit map of which rival mandates are autonomy rungs vs ODD tolerances vs
    genuine dimensions.</li>
  <li><strong>Refresh trigger</strong> — deep-fetch the candidate-only sources (software-factory writeups,
